<img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//a8d1/a8d19b13b74728d383dd65d7da687aa2.com/large/1775000fdc17e6a14a33"> 
<p>适用人群：成人、婴幼儿均适用，分量略不同。</p> 
<img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//0c97/0c97480f9fab4d991eb67036a9ca01e6.com/large/182e000c029d7af63241"> 
